#: ../../M/mumblage.rst:5
msgid "mumblage"
msgstr "mumblage"

#: ../../M/mumblage.rst:7
msgid "/muhm´bl\\@j/, n\\."
msgstr "/muhm´bl\\@j/, 名詞"

#: ../../M/mumblage.rst:9
msgid ""
"The topic of one's mumbling (see :ref:`mumble`\\). \"All that mumblage\" is "
"used like \"all that stuff\" when it is not quite clear how the subject of "
"discussion works, or like \"all that crap\" when ‘mumble’ is being used as "
"an implicit replacement for pejoratives."
msgstr ""
"人がぶつぶつ言っている(\\ :ref:`mumble`\\ を参照)ことの話題。「All that "
"mumblage(あのもろもろのぶつぶつ)」は、議論の主題がどう働くかがあまりはっきりしないときに「all that "
"stuff(あのもろもろ)」のように、あるいは‘mumble’が侮蔑語の暗黙の代用として使われているときに「all that "
"crap(あのもろもろのくそ)」のように使われる。"
